OL,3,CUS intensifies strikes against Iran
OL,4,Cafter reinstating blockade
OL,6,FThe US has reimposed a naval blockade
OL,7,Fon Iran and intensified its airstrike
OL,8,Fcampaign in retaliation for Tehran's
OL,9,Fattacks on ships trying to pass
OL,10,Fthrough the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,12,FThe American strikes hit an Iranian
OL,13,Farmy barracks, killing at least seven
OL,14,Ftroops and wounding hundreds of people
OL,15,Facross the country, Iranian officials
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
