OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784191682
OL,3,CUS intensifies strikes against Iran
OL,4,Cafter reinstating blockade
OL,6,FDays of back-and-forth strikes by the
OL,7,FUS and Iran across the Middle East
OL,8,Fhave shredded the interim deal to end
OL,9,Fthe conflict and sent oil prices
OL,10,Fsoaring.
OL,12,FThe US first imposed a blockade in
OL,13,FApril and lifted it last month after
OL,14,Fsigning the interim deal that paused
OL,15,Fthe fighting and set 60 days for
OL,16,Fnegotiations over issues such as
OL,17,FIran's nuclear programme.
OL,19,FThose talks have stalled as fighting
OL,20,Fover the Strait of Hormuz has
OL,21,Fintensified.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784191682
OL,3,CUS intensifies strikes against Iran
OL,4,Cafter reinstating blockade
OL,6,FWhen the US and Israel launched the
OL,7,Fwar on Iran on February 28, Tehran
OL,8,Feffectively closed the waterway to
OL,9,Fshipping traffic, a move that sent the
OL,10,Fprice of oil, fertiliser and many
OL,11,Fother goods soaring far beyond the
OL,12,Fregion and gave Iran major leverage in
OL,13,Fnegotiations.
OL,15,FDespite repeated efforts from Donald
OL,16,FTrump, the US has struggled to
OL,17,Fsuccessfully reopen the waterway.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
