OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784191682
OL,3,CUS intensifies strikes against Iran
OL,4,Cafter reinstating blockade
OL,6,FTrade did begin to pass through
OL,7,Fbriefly again after the deal was
OL,8,Fsigned, but now it has effectively
OL,9,Fhalted again.
OL,11,FAbout 24 hours after the blockade went
OL,12,Finto effect, the US military opened
OL,13,Ffire on and disabled a merchant vessel
OL,14,Fon Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
