OL,3,CUS intensifies strikes against Iran
OL,4,Cafter reinstating blockade
OL,6,FIran's parliament speaker and lead
OL,7,Fnegotiator, Mohammad Bagher Qalibaf,
OL,8,Fsaid Iran was prepared for a fuller
OL,9,Fmilitary confrontation if the US did
OL,10,Fnot live up to the terms of the
OL,11,Finterim deal, and Iran's paramilitary
OL,12,FRevolutionary Guard threatened to halt
OL,13,Fall energy exports from the Middle
OL,14,FEast over the blockade.
OL,16,FSoon after the US launched its third
OL,17,Fwave of strikes in 24 hours, Trump
OL,18,Fsaid Iran was ready to strike a peace
OL,19,Fdeal, but he did not elaborate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
