OL,3,CUS intensifies strikes against Iran
OL,4,Cafter reinstating blockade
OL,6,FUS Central Command said it spotted
OL,7,FCuracao-flagged oil tanker Belma
OL,8,Fsailing toward Kharg Island and, after
OL,9,Fthe ship "ignored multiple warnings",
OL,10,Fa US aircraft disabled the merchant
OL,11,Fvessel by firing hellfire missiles
OL,12,Finto the ship's smokestack.
OL,14,FIn addition to the now-disabled Belma,
OL,15,Fthe US military said it also had to
OL,16,Fspeak with two other commercial
OL,17,Fvessels, but they complied with their
OL,18,Finstructions to turn away.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
