OL,3,CUS intensifies strikes against Iran
OL,4,Cafter reinstating blockade
OL,6,FThe US military disabled at least
OL,7,Feight merchant vessels during the
OL,8,Ffirst round of the blockade, including
OL,9,Fone strike that left three sailors
OL,10,Fdead.
OL,12,FThe recent strikes have led to a sharp
OL,13,Fincrease in the price of oil.
OL,15,FSubscribe for to our weekly newsletter
OL,16,Ffor exclusive and original coverage
OL,17,Ffrom ITV News. Direct to your inbox
OL,18,Fevery Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
