OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784191682
OL,3,CUS intensifies strikes against Iran
OL,4,Cafter reinstating blockade
OL,6,FThe price for Brent crude oil traded
OL,7,Fabove $85 a barrel on Wednesday, up
OL,8,Ffrom the low $70s at the start of the
OL,9,Fmonth.
OL,11,FAnalysts with the International
OL,12,FMonetary Fund warned Wednesday that
OL,13,Fwhile a surplus of oil had kept prices
OL,14,Flow, "much of that room has now been
OL,15,Fused up."
OL,17,F"Unless inventories are replenished,
OL,18,Fthe world will start from a weaker
OL,19,Fposition when the next shock comes,"
OL,20,FAzim Sadikov and Jean-Marc Natal wrote
OL,21,Fin a blog post.
OL,26,@vD@FOUwD@IO]yD@AOU{D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
