OL,3,CUS intensifies strikes against Iran
OL,4,Cafter reinstating blockade
OL,6,FAccording to the Iranian Health
OL,7,FMinistry, more than 35 people have
OL,8,Fbeen killed and more than 300 wounded
OL,9,Fby US airstrikes in recent days.
OL,11,FIran has responded by striking US
OL,12,Fallies in the region.
OL,14,FMissile-alert warnings sounded
OL,15,FWednesday in Bahrain and Kuwait as
OL,16,Fthey faced incoming Iranian fire - a
OL,17,Fdaily occurrence recently. Jordan said
OL,18,Fit shot down three incoming Iranian
OL,19,Fmissiles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
